products.description: iPhone 16 is built for Apple Intelligence, the personal intelligence system that helps you write, express yourself, and get things done effortlessly. With groundbreaking privacy protections, it gives you peace of mind that no one else can access your data — not even Apple.

Immerse yourself in the action of your favourite games or the beat of your favourite tunes with the Logitech G435 LIGHTSPEED wireless gaming headset. Designed with smaller head sizes in mind, it boasts a lightweight fit to help you stay comfortable for extended playing sessions. It connects wirelessly to a wide range of devices for convenient compatibility.

reviews.review: Very comfortable, but a little expensive.
